data.description: Nestled in a serene corner of Douglasville, GA, lies this exquisite ranch-style home, boasting three bedrooms and two baths. Freshly painted walls and brand-new flooring grace every inch of the house. Stepping inside, you are greeted by a spacious living area that seamlessly flows into the kitchen and dining space. The master bedroom is a haven of tranquility, featuring a stunning master bathroom complete with a large tub, walk-in shower, elegant tiles, and a generously sized walk-in closet. The two additional bedrooms serve as versatile spaces, perfectly suited for either a guest room or a home office. The backyard represents a plethora of possibilities, playing host to a raised deck alongside the rear patio. This area is further accompanied by ample yard space, perfect for gardening and outdoor activities to be enjoyed with loved ones.    HOME ALSO INCLUDES:  - New Tankless Hot Water Heater  - New Floors  - New Roof  - Upscale Floor Moulding  - Gas Appliances
